  "Congratulations! \n\nYou’ve successfully completed all courses in the SDL program. As a reward for your dedication, a digital certificate has been issued to recognize your achievement. You can access and download it via the email linked to your account.\n\nThis certificate highlights your life-saving skills and proves your commitment and expertise.Feel free to share your accomplishment and apply your knowledge in real-life situations. \n\nThank you for your hard work and excellence!": "恭喜您！\n\n您已成功完成SDL訓練的所有課程。為紀念此成就，我們已為您頒發數位結業證書，您可透過註冊於帳戶的電子信箱查看與下載。\n\n這張證書象徵著您在急救與救命技能上的專業與投入。歡迎與身邊的人分享這份成果，並在真實情境中發揮所學。\n\n感謝您的努力與堅持，也再次祝賀您出色地完成課程！",
